Hi Casey,

Sorry about the noise. Two things would help me narrow it down:

1. Paste the X-Clockless-Signature header from one failing call.
2. Confirm whether you also flipped the "active key id" radio on the
   settings page after pasting the new key. There's a known foot-gun
   where the panel saves the new secret but keeps the old key id as
   active, so signatures keep getting computed against the previous
   secret.

If (2) is the issue we can swap it for you in seconds.

Mira

